! Sales Conversion Migration: 100+ Course Technical Lead
''Date:'' August 2018

! Context

Technical lead for functional QA on a 100+ course sales conversion migration from legacy formats (Adobe Presenter, HTML5, Flash) into Xyleme LCMS, published as SCORM 1.2 for Wells Fargo’s enterprise LMS. Six-month engagement, 223 tracked emails. Developed an interactivity-level multiplier methodology for estimating QA effort across the full course portfolio. Diagnosed SCORM completion failures in Flash-based content caused by a race condition in IE’s COM SCORM adapter, compounded by Xyleme’s thin package architecture. Wells Fargo granted full Xyleme Studio administrative access — a direct indicator of client trust.

